{"id":889247941,"lang":"python3","lang_name":"Python3","time":"7 months, 1 week","timestamp":1675234793,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"75 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/889247941/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Longest Substring Without Repeating Characters","memory":"14.1 MB","code":"class Solution:\n    def lengthOfLongestSubstring(self, s: str) -> int:\n        n = len(s)\n        seen = defaultdict(int)\n        global_max = 0\n        l = r = 0\n        while r < n:\n            while seen[s[r]] > 0:\n                seen[s[l]] -= 1\n                l += 1\n            else:\n                seen[s[r]] += 1\n                r += 1\n            global_max = max(global_max, r - l)\n        return global_max","compare_result":"","title_slug":"longest-substring-without-repeating-characters","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
